Custom build of dmenu v5.0
====================
This build uses:
- border (option -bw)
- center (option -c)
- password (option -P)
- xresources (dmenu.font, background => dmenu.background, foreground => dmenu.color4, selbackground => dmenu.color8, selforeground => dmenu.color4)

Requirements
------------
In order to build dmenu you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dmenu is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dmenu
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running dmenu
-------------
See the man page for details.
